-- JFK Airport Terrorism Trial May Go to Jury on July 22, Federal Judge Says
-- Donald Jeffrey
-- 2010-07-15T21:28:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-15/jfk-airport-terrorism-trial-may-go-to-jury-on-july-22-federal-judge-says.html

          
          
             The jury in the trial on an alleged
terrorist plot to destroy John F. Kennedy International Airport
in New York by blowing up fuel lines and tanks may begin
deliberating July 22, the federal judge in the case said today.  
